sequenceDiagram
    participant CME as CME Globex Exchange
    participant DB as DataBento<br/>GLBX.MDP3
    participant DC as databento-client.ts
    participant EN as event-normalizer.ts
    participant EB as Atlas Event Bus
    participant BB as bar-builder.ts
    participant TS as tick-storage.ts
    participant SSE as SSE Fan-Out
    participant DASH as Dashboard<br/>Live Chart

    CME->>DB: Trade executed (nanosecond timestamp)
    DB->>DC: MBP-1 record (action=T, binary DBN)
    DC->>DC: Parse DBN record
    DC->>EN: Raw Mbp1Record
    EN->>EN: Convert price (÷1e9)<br/>Map instrument_id → MNQ1!
    EN->>EB: AtlasTradeEvent { price, size, side, tsEvent, atlasTs }

    par Parallel consumers
        EB->>BB: AtlasTradeEvent
        BB->>BB: Update developing bar OHLCV
        BB->>EB: AtlasBarEvent { status: developing }
        EB->>SSE: AtlasBarEvent developing
        SSE->>DASH: SSE: atlas_bar_developing

        EB->>TS: AtlasTradeEvent
        TS->>TS: INSERT INTO atlas_ticks (async)
    end

    Note over BB,DASH: Developing bar updates at ≤10 updates/sec (100ms rate limit)
